dct_title_s: County map of Utah and Nevada
dct_description_sm: Shows roads, overland telegraph route, and other features.   Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.   Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington.   In lower right corner: 49.   Appears to be from an atlas published by S. Augustus Mitchell, Jr., approximately 1867, page 49.
